# Pem mobile app (`app/`)

**Product:** **dump → organized extracts + thoughts journal**. Primary surface: **`/inbox`** (glance). Voice-first dump, text secondary. **Ask Pem** for Q&A about your data.

## Screens & navigation

- **Navigation:** **expo-router** **`Stack`** (`app/(app)/_layout.tsx`) + **`AppDrawerProvider`** / **`AppDrawerContent`** — full drawer with sections:
  - **Main:** Inbox · Thoughts · Done · Everything
  - **Categories:** Ideas · Someday
  - **Batches:** Shopping · Calls · Emails · Errands
  - **Bottom:** Ask Pem · Settings
- **`thoughts/_layout.tsx`** inner **`Stack`** (list → detail). **`category/[slug].tsx`** dynamic category/batch page.
- **`AppMenuButton`** opens drawer; scrim closes.

## TypeScript & components

- **TypeScript strict** — functional components only.
- **API:** **`lib/pemApi.ts`** — types renamed: `ApiExtract`, `ExtractsQueryParams`, `getExtractsQuery`, `patchExtractDone`, `patchExtractDismiss`, `askPem`, `createVoiceDump`. Routes: `/extracts/...`, `/ask`, `/dumps/voice`.
- **Inbox UI tokens:** **`constants/inboxChrome.ts`** (light/dark glance surfaces); compose with **`ThemeContext`**.
- **Feature folders:** **`components/inbox/`** (glance, dump bar, detail modal), **`components/navigation/`** (drawer + menu button), **`components/ui/`** (`PemListRow`, `PemMindEmptyState`).
- **Voice dump:** **`expo-av`** for recording → **`POST /dumps/voice`** → backend transcription via OpenAI Whisper. Record/pause/end UI. Voice-first, "or type it" toggle.
- **Ask Pem:** **`/ask`** — simple Q&A screen, not chat. User asks about their data, Pem responds.
- **Real-time:** **`hooks/useDumpInboxStream.ts`** after dump → refresh inbox.
- **Timezone:** **`TimezoneRegistrar`** — PATCH **`/users/me/timezone`**.
- **Push:** **`PushNotificationRegistrar`** — **`inbox_updated`** → **`/inbox`**.
- **Thoughts:** Shows polished text only (no original dump shown to user).
- **Brand:** **`constants/theme.ts`**, **`typography.ts`**, **`brand/pem-brand.html`**.

## JSX readability

Prefer named booleans, early returns, small child components. Avoid nested ternary trees.

**Maintenance:** When **routes, UI patterns, tokens, hooks, or API shapes** change, update **this file** in the same effort. See **`pem-project.mdc`**.
